HEADWORD: Steamboat
<hw>Steam"boat`</hw> <pr>(-b⟦omac⟧t`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A boat or
vessel propelled by steam power; -- generally used of river or coasting
craft, as distinguished from ocean steamers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

